produced by tony macaulay , he recorded hits including " do n't give up on us " ( 1976 ) which reached no . 1 in the us and the uk , and " silver lady " ( 1977 ) which also topped the charts in the uk. from 1976 until 1978 , he had five uk top 20 singles and two top 10 albums .

